Please create three regex to match next tasks:
    • the current time in format hh:mm:ss
    
    	^(?:(?:([01]?\d|2[0-3]):)?([0-5]?\d):)?([0-5]?\d)$
    
    • ipv4 address:
    
    	^(?:[0-9]{1,3}\.){3}[0-9]{1,3}$
    
    • whole paragraph of test text. Please pick up any text.
    
    	^.+(?:\n.+)*
